# M8 交易语义搜索 — Embeddings 模糊回忆查账

## 里程碑

**M8** — 将用户历史交易向量化存入 Milvus 独立集合 `billmind_transactions`；Agent `search_similar_transactions` + REST 检索；记账/导入后可选增量 upsert。

## 关联 Skill

| Skill | 用途 |
|-------|------|
| [add-api-endpoint](../Skills/add-api-endpoint/SKILL.md) | `GET /transactions/search` |
| [http-integration-test](../Skills/http-integration-test/SKILL.md) | transactions_search_test |
| [local-dev](../Skills/local-dev/SKILL.md) | Milvus + Ollama 本地验收 |
| [extract-ai-knowledge](../Skills/extract-ai-knowledge/SKILL.md) | `docs/knowledge/txn-semantic-search.md` |

## 范围

### 交付文件

| 文件 | 说明 |
|------|------|
| `agent/rag/txn.py` | `TransactionSearch`：sync / search / upsert / delete |
| `agent/rag/txn_index.py` | CLI 全量同步 `--account-id` / `--force` |
| `agent/rag/txn_test.py` | `txn_to_text()` 单测 |
| `agent/skills/transactions_semantic.py` | `search_similar_transactions` skill |
| `agent/agent/promt/system.py` | 语义 vs SQL skill 分流规则 |
| `common/env.py` | `TXN_SEARCH_INCREMENTAL`、`ollama_embedding_ready` |
| `server/api/transactions.py` | `GET /transactions/search` |
| `server/model/response/transaction_search.py` | 检索响应模型 |
| `examples/05_txn_semantic_demo.py` | 独立 demo |
| `docs/knowledge/txn-semantic-search.md` | M8 知识点 |

### Phase 2（本 plan 含）

- `add_transaction` / `import_csv_transactions` 成功后 `maybe_upsert*`（受 `TXN_SEARCH_INCREMENTAL` 控制）

## 知识点文档

| slug | 文件 | 验收 |
|------|------|------|
| `txn-semantic-search` | `docs/knowledge/txn-semantic-search.md` | README 索引 status → done |

## 运行命令

```bash
docker compose up -d ollama milvus
.venv/bin/python3.14 -m agent.rag.txn_index --account-id 1
.venv/bin/python3.14 examples/05_txn_semantic_demo.py
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" "http://127.0.0.1:8000/transactions/search?q=星巴克"
.venv/bin/python3.14 -m pytest agent/rag/txn_test.py server/api/transactions_search_test.py -v
```

## 验收标准

- [x] `pytest agent/rag/txn_test.py -v` 通过
- [x] 账号有 Starbucks 记录时 demo / `GET /transactions/search?q=星巴克` 能命中
- [x] Agent `search_similar_transactions` 未就绪时返回 JSON 错误而非 500
- [x] `TXN_SEARCH_INCREMENTAL=0` 可关闭记账后自动 upsert
- [x] `docs/knowledge/txn-semantic-search.md` 存在
